---
title: Courgette and Sun-Dried Tomato Tart with Rocket Salad
description: Pastry might seem like it’s the preserve of people who have way too much time on their hands but tonight we’re making it easy*! And here’s some HelloFresh trivia for you … during the drying process sun-dried tomatoes can loose up to 93% of their weight! At the same time the flavours become concentrated to give you that delicious hit of sweetness.
*Step aside Mary Berry!
